<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN298-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai – karantai; tuṟai – neṭumoḻi. āliyār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN298">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>emakkē kalaṅka ṟarumē tāṉē</l>
<l>tēṟa luṇṇu maṉṉē naṉṟu</l>
<l>miṉṉāṉ maṉṟa vēntē yiṉiyē</l>
<l>nērā rāreyiṉ muṟṟi</l>
<l>vāymaṭit turaṟinī munteṉ ṉāṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>To us, he will give turbid [licquor]. He himself</l>
<l>will drink clarified toddy. Pretty </l>
<l>unpleasant is the king. [But] now,</l>
<l>having put an end to the difficult fortress of the enemies,</l>
<l>pursing [his] mouth, he won’t shout “you in front”.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
